      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\u2022  GET /api/usage \u2192 today/month cents + by-feature breakdown.\n\u2022  1 receipt \u2248 $0.0028; 300-row statement \u2248 2.9\u00a2 (verified).\n\u2022  Set MAX_DAILY_COST_CENTS low to confirm the cap blocks further calls.",
